{"tid":1346452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求組自發性市民救助團隊 求文宣人 admin 聯絡統籌","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T05:12:51.000Z","uid":263165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c65ec4f7a92018580c73a1c7609e0b9161932128","tid":1346452,"uid":263165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:12:30.000Z","msg":"自己救自己<br />\n強烈建議自組自衛團隊<br />\n自衛團隊既最主要目的係保護市民 互助為目的<br />\n小弟不才只能概括d講<br />\n1）不戀戰 不進攻 保護自身安全 並明白風險<br />\n2）避免刺激/攻擊來襲者 以免自身及同行者受到不必要既襲擊<br />\n3）只在有鏡頭保障同有把握既情況下行使「自衛權」將來襲者制服<br />\n4）盡快按序撤離<br />\n5）在無法撒離既情況下 集中固守一個地方<br />\n求各路人才<br />\nTG link: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/D8VO8BQDtfjKudR5UB70HQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FD8VO8BQDtfjKudR5UB70HQ&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=7855d9a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/D8VO8BQDtfjKudR5UB70HQ</a>"},{"pid":"79c894ecef575d83550092597b7701850a3af016","tid":1346452,"uid":263165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:23:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df24ad6c41f812eec26198d0d6073c0df3bd4e80","tid":1346452,"uid":265434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:32:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"815df0a1a0d3fe1198783dd095c286873296cd98","tid":1346452,"uid":151583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1005e572d50bf8d3292241f6daccad31ce4e5b77","tid":1346452,"uid":284000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:06:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ec5e14690a11cd0bcbf64362ba88301b54fbbd8","tid":1346452,"uid":262485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}